Vintage 14K Yellow Gold Flower Ring with Blue Enamel and Diamonds

About the Item

Vintage 14K Yellow Gold Flower Ring with Blue Enamel and Diamonds - The ring contains 1 round brilliant diamond in each of the 6 blue enamel flowers with a total approximate weight of .33ct. The diamonds are G - H colour and VS2 - SI1 clarity. The top of the ring measures 17.5mm in diameter and the height is 10mm off the finger. The ring is a size 6.75 and can be resized upon request. The ring weighs 7.5 grammes.
